{"tid":1185002,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人毒到每日都當玩RPG game咁過？","createTime":"2019-06-04T03:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T08:40:48.000Z","uid":46947,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"296fad39cafa655220a6c1b7df26751055dca09e","tid":1185002,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"行街仲要唱埋隻game冒險配樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc11dd51dcf06c35ac62cc5c1561dd446783c17d","tid":1185002,"uid":46947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"每日不停去詢問、收集情報、補血、補眠、賺金幣，有時仲會同路人甲乙丙丁嘈交郁手郁腳、買裝甲、鞋仔、魔法、藥草&hellip;&hellip;隻game真係好煩好難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b671d7b17fe6e9766db5896a28d293db59ed2e","tid":1185002,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"遊戲人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95285b0f8c81da3dbd3a219a6378b434deb48e4a","tid":1185002,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"我想不斷按休息"},{"pid":"546f10ffc272b574ee4d92c777ded33a3dd00b41","tid":1185002,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:00:29.000Z","msg":"咩game"},{"pid":"0bf4e137ffa593f333d1903d86c29a5c5d7bfb27","tid":1185002,"uid":227091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"317de231dfd8d8a62d1dbb1988047956299b658a","tid":1185002,"uid":19095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"咁都幾開心吖"},{"pid":"79f97868b5c62c47aac07d77065bd29f63cc3aa5","tid":1185002,"uid":90259,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"冇，但有當過rpg係日常生活咁玩<br />\n<br />\nSkyrim入到驚就係做一個農夫<br />\n每日耕田種菜，然後斬柴賣俾附近旅店老闆幫補家計<br />\n隔幾日就有士兵過黎收稅，賺埋嘅錢俾晒俾地咁濟<br />\n唯一娛樂係隔晚去旅店嗌杯酒同份燉肉，聽下吟遊詩人唱歌<br />\n經常聽啲村民講邊個洞穴有山賊，邊度有屍鬼墓地，裡邊收埋好多寶藏<br />\n但對連野狼都打唔贏嘅我根本遙不可及，我想嘅係有朝一日儲夠錢，同個19領主買塊地，起返間自己嘅沾吼，唔駛同啲礦工逼埋一齊訓狗竇<br />\n為左達成夢想，我膽粗粗走去屍鬼墓地，一路靠潛行唔打淨係執野<br />\n執到滿諗住返屋企時俾堆狼圍，由於拎得太多走唔快，最後俾狼群咬死左<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係我最後一次玩Skyrim"},{"pid":"967db7d58b556acb02271314363ff5adb0fab37a","tid":1185002,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"今日攪咗半日都換唔倒寶藏（集齊唔倒申請所需文件），走嚟走去，途中勁多怪獸要避開（哼住撞倒怪獸啲音樂嚟行）屌又真係好撚毒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b64c77a8e3a6bb068c84d15b794c274484ba6e","tid":1185002,"uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"你只係其中一個每日做相同野既npc"},{"pid":"a0248a6dfe677b32f5368e1dad901395aa85c146","tid":1185002,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"做緊路邊個NPC<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2912d1586d11db57987df93ce2bd1ea00ea0dd06","tid":1185002,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"毒到玩rpg改到99lv玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da3b15ff9053cc8738445a80c673ace033e2b4b","tid":1185002,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"冇得入人屋開箱仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a6e1b9a97a6160149377cb53a7145b349117da","tid":1185002,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"淨係識做人   屌你"},{"pid":"3766fbac361893254ef2dea4f16da75d06c8ac6a","tid":1185002,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"完啦個post...<br />\n好撚on9"},{"pid":"65dbec1cf5716e61189113e8bbaa2d83b41fb2e6","tid":1185002,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"Game developers 好似setting到比少左個女主角<img src=\"/assets